These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
City: colone, rome, paris, nizza
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person traveling to rome is the fan of techno##1
2. the person traveling to paris is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person traveling to rome is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| City   | nizza | rome | paris | colone |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

