The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, sailing, tennis
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, salsa, punk, trance
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##2
 6. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the fan of punk##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | cherry  | cucumber | kale     | carrot     |
| Pet         | hamster | goldfish | goat     | guinea-pig |
| Sport       | rowing  | tennis   | biathlon | sailing    |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | salsa   | disco  | trance        |

